mkdir ~/.conky
copy .conkyrc_1, .conkyrc_2, conky_start & wan_ip to .conky/
make sure conky_start & wan_ip are executable
Add to start up: bash -c "sleep 10; /home/jerry/.conky/conky_start"

.conkyrc_2 is for the onboard wireless (wlan0)
.conkyrc_2_ra0 is for the Netgear WNDA 4100 Dual Band adapter (ra0)